#. <section class="sutta" id="sn19.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn19.21:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 19"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 19"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.21:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 21. Pāpasāmaṇerīsutta → sāmaṇerīsuttaṃ (bj) | sāmaṇeriyo (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Pāpasāmaṇerīsutta"
msgstr "21. A Bad Female Novice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.21:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ sāmaṇeriṃ vehāsaṃ "
"gacchantiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw "
"a female novice flying through the air."

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tassā saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto "
"sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāyabandhanampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ "
"sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr "Her outer robe, bowl, belt, and body were burning, blazing, and glowing"

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.3"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti."
msgstr "as she screamed in pain."

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi:"
msgstr "It occurred to me:"

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.5"
msgid "‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho."
msgstr "‘It’s incredible, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.6"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma satto bhavissati."
msgstr "That there can be such a sentient being,"

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.7"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma yakkho bhavissati."
msgstr "such an entity,"

msgctxt "sn19.21:1.8"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma attabhāvapaṭilābho bhavissatī’”ti."
msgstr "such an incarnation!’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.262"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.21:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.2"
msgid "“cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are disciples who live full of vision and knowledge,"

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.3"
msgid ""
"ñāṇabhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti, yatra hi nāma sāvako evarūpaṃ "
"ñassati vā dakkhati vā sakkhiṃ vā karissati."
msgstr "since a disciple knows, sees, and witnesses such a thing."

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.4"
msgid "Pubbeva me sā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī diṭṭhā ahosi."
msgstr "Formerly, I too saw that female novice, but I did not speak of it."

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.5"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ na byākāsiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.6"
msgid "Ahañcetaṃ byākareyyaṃ, pare ca me na saddaheyyuṃ."
msgstr "For if I had spoken of it others would not have believed me,"

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.7"
msgid "Ye me na saddaheyyuṃ, tesaṃ taṃ assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "which would be for their lasting harm and suffering."

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.8"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī kassapassa sammāsambuddhassa pāvacane pāpasāmaṇerī "
"ahosi."
msgstr ""
"That female novice used to be a bad female novice in the time of the Buddha "
"Kassapa’s dispensation."

msgctxt "sn19.21:2.9"
msgid ""
"Sā tassa kammassa vipākena bahūni vassāni bahūni vassasatāni bahūni "
"vassasahassāni bahūni vassasatasahassāni niraye paccitvā tasseva kammassa "
"vipākāvasesena evarūpaṃ attabhāvapaṭilābhaṃ paṭisaṃvedayatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"As a result of that deed she burned in hell for many years, many hundreds, "
"many thousands, many hundreds of thousands of years. Now she experiences the "
"residual result of that deed in such an incarnation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.21:2.10"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.21:2.11"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.1"
msgid "Kūpe nimuggo hi so pāradāriko,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.2"
msgid "Gūthakhādi ahu duṭṭhabrāhmaṇo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.3"
msgid "Nicchavitthi aticārinī ahu,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.4"
msgid "Maṅgulitthi ahu ikkhaṇitthikā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.5"
msgid "Okilini sapattaṅgārokiri,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:3.6"
msgid "Sīsacchinno ahu coraghātako."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.21:4.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu bhikkhunī sikkhamānā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:4.2"
msgid "Sāmaṇero atha sāmaṇerikā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:4.3"
msgid "Kassapassa vinayasmiṃ pabbajjaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn19.21:4.4"
msgid "Pāpakammaṃ kariṃsu tāvadeti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn19.21:4.5"
msgid "Lakkhaṇasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with Lakkhaṇa are complete."
